2:T7a4,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Jasper Chat better than Microsoft Copilot?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Jasper Chat scores 6.0 overall while Microsoft Copilot scores 7.0. Jasper Chat is best for marketing teams and brand-voice chat, while Microsoft Copilot excels for Office 365 users and enterprise."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Jasper Chat or Microsoft Copilot?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Jasper Chat starts at $49/mo and Microsoft Copilot starts at Free.  Microsoft Copilot offers a free plan. Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Jasper Chat to Microsoft Copilot?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Jasper Chat and Microsoft Copilot support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Jasper Chat vs Microsoft Copilot?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Jasper Chat holds an overall rating of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10. Microsoft Copilot has an overall rating of 7/10 and ease of use score of 8/10. Users praise Jasper Chat for trained on marketing best practices and Microsoft Copilot for deep microsoft 365 integration."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Jasper Chat or Microsoft Copilot?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Microsoft Copilot for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Jasper Chat remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize trained on marketing best practices. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"oWPZTPCPUwZMl312gxRMA",